1147.name: CuZn40F
1147.Applications: Mainly used in the furniture and the bicycle industry
1147.Suitable_For: Brazing: Steels, Copper, Cast iron, Copper alloys, Nickel and for welding Brass and Bronze. This alloy is mainly used in the furniture and the bicycle industry for joining steels, also this alloy can be used for rebuilding Brass- ship propellers by flame welding.
